name: FRigVMGraphVariableDescription
doc:
The variable description is used to convey information
about unique variables within a Graph. Multiple Variable
Nodes can share the same variable description.

Name: FName
The name of the variable
CPPType: The C++ data type of the variable
CPPTypeObject: The Struct of the C++ data type of the variable (or nullptr)
DefaultValue: The default value of the variable
